<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Increase2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Increase,</orth> vb. 1) trans. to augment, to make grow, to make more or greater: <bibl n="shak. son 64.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 64, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 78</bibl>. Tw, <bibl n="shak. mm 1.5.85" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.161" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 161</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.183" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.5.235" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 235</bibl> (or == to make thrive?). <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.100" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 7, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 97</bibl>.<lb />2) intr. to become more and greater: <bibl n="shak. ven 254" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 254</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 15.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 15, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 107</bibl> (== thriving). <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.205" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 205</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.2.104" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.48" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.507" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 507</bibl> (Ff <emph>grows strong</emph>). <bibl n="shak. cor 5.2.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 2, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.216" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 216</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.196" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 2, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 60</bibl>.
